data.description: Welcome to your new home in the highly desirable Bristol Township at under 300k ! This home sits on a huge lot on a quiet dead end street. This 3 bed 2 bath home  was well maintained with new carpets in the living room and hallways.  Cozy up this winter with the nice fireplace!  The primary and  2nd bedrooms are generous in size! The 3rd bedroom has ample space as well. Possible 4th bedroom/office directly across from that bedroom. This home boasts a finished basement with a fully finished bathroom. 6 car driveway and plenty of street parking! The huge backyard is a must see! schedule your tour today and come see this home for yourself!
